/>\n去做你想做既範疇"},{"pid":"154f33c3096e34888c3a3f6daefa5a2981f24916","tid":182260,"uid":22005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T10:05:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>泥水啦<br />\n<br />\n入行人工都唔錯<br />\n<br />\n係污漕少少<br />\n<br />\n至少唔洗點晒</blockquote><br />\n泥水又真係污糟啲<br />\n<br />\n小弟噴油，跟老細</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n小弟冷電 hea下hea下又一工"},{"pid":"0abb2f1525705eb3105c8f8b410f712203032308","tid":182260,"uid":1024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T10:09:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>泥水啦<br />\n<br />\n入行人工都唔錯<br />\n<br />\n係污漕少少<br />\n<br />\n至少唔洗點晒</blockquote><br />\n泥水又真係污糟啲<br />\n<br />\n小弟噴油，跟老細</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n小弟冷電 hea下hea下又一工</blockquote><br />\n水電點睇？"},{"pid":"ce4a90ede9d4922a9ca071ef04f6143d9155c4c7","tid":182260,"uid":17906,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T10:10:15.000Z","msg":"我都係由sales 轉地盤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之前份sales 又做到隻狗咁<br />\n咁不知去地盤涯下好過<br />\n起碼時間好用左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n做左大半年電燈仔"},{"pid":"0c4bc2f41a54ce61c4dd1b1efb2213956685e63b","tid":182260,"uid":49071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T10:21:37.000Z","msg":"如果想做但唔識人咁點"},{"pid":"bb39c4459aeb42207305052aefad1dacc2e87f9a","tid":182260,"uid":17906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T10:25:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>如果想做但唔識人咁點</blockquote><br />\nFB 搵地盤group<br />\n睇下自己想做邊氾<br />\n時不時都有人搵白紙<br />\n不過預左可能俾人食少少<br />\n例如識人可能有$700 一工<br />\n唔識人可能會$600~650 一工"},{"pid":"1af16558dd32d1d597af07cb811946395cb07ef3","tid":182260,"uid":47338,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T10:28:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>泥水啦<br />\n<br />\n入行人工都唔錯<br />\n<br />\n係污漕少少<br />\n<br />\n至少唔洗點晒</blockquote><br />\n泥水又真係污糟啲<br />\n<br />\n小弟噴油，跟老細</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n小弟冷電 hea下hea下又一工</blockquote><br />\n水電點睇？</blockquote><br />\n有前途，不過都係果句，識人/有老細照唔同好多<br />\n<br />\n我自己就唔打公司工，直接跟老細，等佢安排<br />\n唔驚冇工開（前提要係好老細）"},{"pid":"c2da377782ee5cec3ab944a8b4fb1281e100c197","tid":182260,"uid":47338,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T10:31:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我都係由sales 轉地盤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之前份sales 又做到隻狗咁<br />\n咁不知去地盤涯下好過<br />\n起碼時間好用左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n做左大半年電燈仔</blockquote><br />\n時間好用咗係真，冇得輸<br />\n就算ot都計1.5，明碼實價<br />\n星期日/紅日想返就返，輕輕鬆鬆又一工<br />\n<br />\n之前做倉，搏命上咗位，加得$300，我屌咗出黎<br />\n即走"},{"pid":"6b793acc0c661e5c4f55bddc02dccfc9a7fd8dce","tid":182260,"uid":7843,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T10:36:35.000Z","msg":"巴打加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94e4d3924a83a84edd1a3c5b832136bf1fc01b72","tid":182260,"uid":31178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T10:42:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>泥水啦<br />\n<br />\n入行人工都唔錯<br />\n<br />\n係污漕少少<br />\n<br />\n至少唔洗點晒</blockquote><br />\n泥水又真係污糟啲<br />\n<br />\n小弟噴油，跟老細</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n小弟冷電 hea下hea下又一工</blockquote><br />\n水電點睇？</blockquote><br />\n有前途，不過都係果句，識人/有老細照唔同好多<br />\n<br />\n我自己就唔打公司工，直接跟老細，等佢安排<br />\n唔驚冇工開（前提要係好老細）</blockquote><br />\n識電燈師傅實收1200一工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6467e2ceb82a492d451787b0fb690ed90153692","tid":182260,"uid":93687,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T10:46:22.000Z","msg":"咩Sales得萬得咁少"},{"pid":"10a7b707319ee0e2f927552dacb145f6aa09219c","tid":182260,"uid":55989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T10:46:47.000Z","msg":"想問下可以點入行"},{"pid":"12cf04f0bf23898834d301f83f7895db62ba44ba","tid":182260,"uid":71433,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"re